des: Dominaria facts contains random facts about the lore of the Dominaria plane, the largest universe of Magic the Gathering Multiverse. Some of these facts will link different cards you use when playing the card game. The information provided comes mostly from the Wizard of the Coast publication and Flavor Text of actual cards.
